Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.27,1:47:02.50,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Furimuita sono ushiro no Shoumen daare?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.56,1:47:10.49,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurayami ni tsume o tatete yoru o hikisaita
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.49,1:47:19.88,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Amadare wa chi no shizuku to natte hoho o tsutai ochiru
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.88,1:47:29.78,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou doko ni mo kaeru basho ga nai nara
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.78,1:47:34.47,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono yubi tomare watashi no yubi ni
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.47,1:47:39.36,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono yubi goto tsurete tte ageru
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.36,1:47:43.87,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Higurashi ga naku akazu no mori e
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.87,1:47:49.82,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Atomodori wa mou dekinai
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.27,1:47:02.50,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa obzrieš za seba, kto tam bude stáť?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.56,1:47:10.49,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak zatneš prsty do temnoty, môžeš roztrhať noc.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.49,1:47:19.88,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvapky dažďa sa zmenia na krv ktorá ti steká po tvári
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.88,1:47:29.78,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,a ty sa už nebudeš mať kam vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.78,1:47:34.47,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Stačí len, ak sa ma chytíš jediným prstom
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.47,1:47:39.36,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,a ja ťa odtiaľ odvediem preč.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.36,1:47:43.87,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Za miestom kde večer v lese plačú cikády,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.87,1:47:49.82,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}sa však už nesmieš obzrieť späť.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.82,1:47:53.95,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukedashitette nukedashitette
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.95,1:47:58.93,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanashisugiru unmei kara
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.93,1:48:04.97,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa naraku no hana ja nai
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.97,1:48:07.04,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna basho de
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.04,1:48:11.55,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakanaide sakanaide
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.55,1:48:17.62,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Karametorarete ikanaide
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.62,1:48:25.64,opromaleft,,0000,0000,0000,,Oto mo naku tobikau toki no kakera
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.82,1:47:53.95,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Utekaj, utekaj,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.95,1:47:58.93,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,uteč pred svojim nešťastným osudom.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.93,1:48:04.97,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty nie si kvet na dne priepasti.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.97,1:48:07.04,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekvitni tam, nekvitni tam,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.04,1:48:11.55,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,na tom smutnom mieste.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.55,1:48:17.62,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenechaj sa znova chytiť.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.62,1:48:25.64,opromaright,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj úlomky času potichu letieť okolo nás.
